		<outline text="June 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="june2021" >
			<outline text="June 28" type="calendarDay" name="28" >
				<outline text="#VenmoMe @Jennifer-Neal-20 https://t.co/h7aRAHeRF7" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 18:11:21 GMT" tweetId="1409575159866920961" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409575159866920961" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 27" type="calendarDay" name="27" >
				<outline text=".@onepeloton when are the VR headsets coming?  During my run this morning, I also thought: Imagine being on the bike, but *riding* this route with @jesskingnyc and sharing all the #joy and PRIDE. xo" type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 21:22:48 GMT" tweetId="1409260953141530626" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409260953141530626" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="This morning I did a *run* with @jesskingnyc in my ears and my heart along the entire Pride Parade route in #NYC. It was pure magic. We should be proud to show up exactly as we are https://t.co/3WiOT3SoeF. #loveislove https://t.co/6eaEdH99Pl" type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 21:06:25 GMT" tweetId="1409256828886601731" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1409256828886601731" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 26" type="calendarDay" name="26" >
				<outline text="All those years I have showed up at weddings #naked.  I've been doing it wrong! #truestory https://t.co/AXviF5p6SM" type="tweet" created="Sat, 26 Jun 2021 18:51:21 GMT" tweetId="1408860450394017800" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1408860450394017800" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 23" type="calendarDay" name="23" >
				<outline text="I signed up for the SCHRUTE FARMS BED &amp;amp; BREAKFAST 5K/10K!  It's like these people have actually met me or something??  

 https://t.co/7CC54h0DEh https://t.co/7CC54h0DEh" type="tweet" created="Wed, 23 Jun 2021 21:22:58 GMT" tweetId="1407811440904261632" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1407811440904261632" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				<outline text="I have a #NYC phone number.  I received over 30 calls/texts yesterday reminding me to #vote. 

That's a lot of robots." type="tweet" created="Wed, 23 Jun 2021 15:57:03 GMT" tweetId="1407729422304641037" urltweet="https://twitter.com/nakedjen/status/1407729422304641037" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="nakedjen" />
				</outline>
